elf:data:0x0023980C,ram:0x08A3D80C,size::
The corridor extends far back. A huge duct
runs parallel with it...
elf:data:0x0023985C,ram:0x08A3D85C,size::
The corridor became less steep.
Because of the dim lightning,
I could step on some wiring...
elf:data:0x002398A8,ram:0x08A3D8A8,size::
The air gradually became colder.
The passage is getting wider...
elf:data:0x002398E8,ram:0x08A3D8E8,size::
I emerged into a bright corridor.
The ceiling was high and equipment
lifts were moving...
elf:data:0x00239938,ram:0x08A3D938,size::
While turning left through a
narrow hatch, a mouse
ran through my feet...
elf:data:0x00239988,ram:0x08A3D988,size::
Turning right, the passage was
filled with debris. I advanced
by going around the debris...
elf:data:0x002399D4,ram:0x08A3D9D4,size::
After climbing a ladder, I opened
a hatch to another compartment. I
look around and close the hatch.
elf:data:0x00239A34,ram:0x08A3DA34,size::
After climbing a long ladder, I was
in a huge dark space. I search
for where I'm headed...
elf:data:0x00239A8C,ram:0x08A3DA8C,size::
After ignoring a side door, I
came to a low ceiling, and proceeded
while hunched over.
elf:data:0x00239AEC,ram:0x08A3DAEC,size::
After inserting the %s, there's
a light mechanical sound, and
the door opens...
elf:data:0x00239B28,ram:0x08A3DB28,size::
After inserting the %s, it took
a while to authenticate, but
it unlocks and the door opens...
elf:data:0x00239B78,ram:0x08A3DB78,size::
Passed %s through a card reader with
a Seele seal. A huge door
quietly opens...
elf:data:0x00239D18,ram:0x08A3DD18,size::
No good, it can't be unlocked
with an ID card you have now...
elf:data:0x00239D78,ram:0x08A3DD78,size:: Huh, of all the places to come out.
elf:data:0x00239DB0,ram:0x08A3DDB0,size::
At this dead end, there's exposed wiring
and what appears to be a direct terminal
to Magi...
elf:data:0x00239E14,ram:0x08A3DE14,size::
When the corridor opens up, there's an
abandoned shooting range. The guns
and ammo are all pristine though...
